      • getDBCountries

        public static void getDBCountries()
        The getDBCountries() method. This method searches the database with the use of a SELECT statement to find all the countries in the countries table. It will pull the data in and create a Country object and adds the object to the allCountries list. The list is cleared each time that it is ran to avoid multiple entries of the same objects.
